{"word":"Azmaveth","slug":"azmaveth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Azmaveth</b> <a href=\"#/H5820\">H5820</a> <br/> 1. One of David's heroes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=31'>2Sa 23:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=33'>1Ch 11:33</a><br/> 2. A descendant of Jonathan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=36'>1Ch 8:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=42'>1Ch 9:42</a><br/> 3. Son of Adiel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=25'>1Ch 27:25</a><br/> 4. A village of Judah or Benjamin<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=24'>Ezr 2:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=29'>Neh 12:29</a> <br/> - Called Beth-Azmaveth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=28'>Neh 7:28</a> "}]}